reviewText: This title was a gift for a friend. He enjoys these animal films and has me order them for himwhen I can.
Top ten animal behavior show that appeals to young kids and adults. Educational, humorous, one of Animal Planets best shows ever!
One of my favorite shows since childhood
Totally love it and so do my kids.  I watch it too because I learn so much.  Everyone learns from this video.
How many shows appeal to 40yr old men and 13yr old girls?  My whole family loves this show!
The best animals based list show I've ever seen!
I love this show! Its kind of corny but it's so interesting and who doesn't love animal shows !
I don't like the format. It tries to sensationalize everything. Very disappointing.
Most (if not all) of the shows I have seen on Animal Planet in the past but it's enjoyable to watch them again. Interesting trivia.
